title: MultiConverter-UnitConverter_1_0_9
description:
Multiconverter is a fully featured unit
converter & calculator offering various
units convertions on android phone.
It has an easy to use Interface
Features:
1. Universar Unit Convertion
* 1250+ units in 65 + categories
* Currency exchange rates (online update with current rates)
2. Customizing for unit/Categories and Currencies
* option for user to select favorite categories
* option for user to select favorite units in categories
* option for user to select favorite Currencies
3. User-defined Units Pairs
* User-defined Units Pairs.
4.calculator
* customized on-screen keyboard
* direct algebraic calculation
** Soon in Next Update User Defined Categories/Units
